  - Pull image from Docker Hub:
    - docker pull ubuntu
    - docker pull alpine
    - docker pull centos
  - Run container (pulls if absent and runs):
    - docker run hello-world
    - Example: docker run ubuntu (will start a container from ubuntu; to run interactively, see -it below)
  - Typical interactive/run flags shown or referenced:
    - docker run -it ubuntu /bin/bash   (interactive shell)
